## 🎯 Research Objectives

### Primary Question
What is the quantifiable relationship between trade openness and national economic growth across different countries and time periods?

### Secondary Questions
- Do developed and developing economies exhibit different trade-growth dynamics?
- How has the trade-growth nexus evolved post-2008 financial crisis?
- Which countries demonstrate optimal trade-growth outcomes and why?

